    <abstract id="aspace_59f64adc51915580065df9c41b270579">The diary of Roger Gill, a Quaker, documenting his trip to the American colonies in 1698 and 1699. The diary describes his travels to Quaker settlements in Long Island, New Jersey, Connecticut, Rhode Island, and other parts of the northeast. Roger Gill died in Philadelphia, PA in 1699.</abstract>
